- C-C single bond length: $r_s = 1.53$ Å
- C-C double bond length: $r_d = 1.335$ Å
- Force constant (single): $k_s = 500$ N/m
- Force constant (double): $k_d = 950$ N/m
- Number of each type: 3 bonds each

