- Condition: (1-x)/x ≥ 2
- This gives: 1-x ≥ 2x
- Therefore: 1 ≥ 3x
- So: x ≤ 1/3

**Case 2: x ≥ 0.5** (so 1-x is the shorter segment)
- Shorter segment: 1-x
- Longer segment: x
- Condition: x/(1-x) ≥ 2
- This gives: x ≥ 2(1-x)
- Therefore: x ≥ 2 - 2x
- So: 3x ≥ 2
- Therefore: x ≥ 2/3

